{"tid":1350173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"事到如今，大家一定要保護元朗警員家人","createTime":"2019-07-22T12:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:28:45.000Z","uid":184854,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e50f6d32c1683af305e1fbafca4446587a7f8d85","tid":1350173,"uid":184854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"冤有頭債有主，牛屎佬做嘢，真係唔關元朗班警察事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋嘅屋企人老婆老公老豆老母更加仲無辜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到鄉土同babykingdom好多網民話要搵佢哋祭旗，我覺得連登仔應該要仗義保護老弱婦孺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有999報案中心接線警員嘅家人，都必須保護好。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察已經唔會保護普通市民嫁喇，要保護呢班警隊家屬，惟有靠我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人有地址呀？"},{"pid":"7dae3aa215377ed349d9019238e168549d4f661b","tid":1350173,"uid":184854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"以武制暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保護警屬"},{"pid":"415c63a8dc9eb29737502c501bd3d10d56cf4d18","tid":1350173,"uid":210778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"快d接佢地<br />\n狗公/ 乸番緊工 屋企沒人睇住好危險嫁<br />\n要發揮香港人     互助互愛      既精神"},{"pid":"7198b556f7287815d69ff35d484a427c3048c041","tid":1350173,"uid":184854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"415c63a8dc9eb29737502c501bd3d10d56cf4d18","tid":1350173,"uid":210778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"快d接佢地<br />\n狗公/ 乸番緊工 屋企沒人睇住好危險嫁<br />\n要發揮香港人     互助互愛      既精神"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"要喺警員屋企樓下接返工放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e265e8faa1d6c7d655385f051d019b167c91902c","tid":1350173,"uid":184854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"以武制暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma